data.title: Charlie Villanueva - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Charlie Villanueva: his birthday, what he did before fame, his family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

NBA power forward known for his three-point shooting; drafted 7th overall by the Toronto Raptors in 2005, spent three years with the Milwaukee Bucks and signed a 5-year deal with the Detroit Pistons in 2009.

Before Fame

He played two years of college basketball at UConn, winning an NCAA Championship in 2004.

Trivia

He began wearing the #31 on his jersey as a tribute to Reggie Miller, his hero growing up.

Family Life

He was born to Roberto Villanueva and Doris Mejia. In 2014, he got engaged to Michelle Game. He and Michelle welcomed a daughter in 2015. He also has a son from a previous relationship.
